<h3 id=3D"20000steps">How many miles is 20,000 steps?</h3>
<p>
<strong>20,000 steps convert to about 9 miles.</strong> Your step length sh=
ould be factored in for an accurate calculation. A woman of average height=
=20
(5ft 4in) walking 20,000 steps at a regular walking speed will travel about=
 8.6 miles, whilst a man of average height (5ft 9in) will walk about 9 mile=
s.
</p>

<a href=3D"https://www.thecalculatorsite.com/health/steps-miles.php#faq" re=
l=3D"nofollow" class=3D"returnToList"><svg><use xlink:href=3D"#arrowTurnUp"=
></use></svg></a>
<h3 id=3D"15000steps">How many miles is 15,000 steps?</h3>
<p>
<strong>15,000 steps convert to about 6 =C2=BE miles.</strong> For a more a=
ccurate calculation, factor in your step length. A woman of average height=
=20
(5ft 4in) walking 15,000 steps at a regular walking speed will travel about=
 6.5 miles, whilst a man of average height (5ft 9in) will walk about 6 =C2=
=BE miles.
</p>

<a href=3D"https://www.thecalculatorsite.com/health/steps-miles.php#faq" re=
l=3D"nofollow" class=3D"returnToList"><svg><use xlink:href=3D"#arrowTurnUp"=
></use></svg></a>
<h3 id=3D"10000steps">How many miles is 10,000 steps?</h3>
<p>
<strong>10,000 steps convert to about 4 =C2=BD miles</strong> at a moderate=
 walking pace of 3 mph. At this pace=20
you will <a href=3D"https://www.thecalculatorsite.com/health/how-long-to-wa=
lk-a-mile">walk a mile in around 20 minutes</a>.To gain a more accurate mea=
surement for the distance you=20
have covered, your height, gender and walking speed need to be factored int=
o the equation.
</p>

<a href=3D"https://www.thecalculatorsite.com/health/steps-miles.php#faq" re=
l=3D"nofollow" class=3D"returnToList"><svg><use xlink:href=3D"#arrowTurnUp"=
></use></svg></a>
<h3 id=3D"5000steps">How many miles is 5,000 steps?</h3>
<p>
<strong>5,000 steps convert to about 2 =C2=BC miles.</strong> Your step len=
gth should be considered when looking for an accurate conversion. A woman o=
f average height=20
(5ft 4in) walking 5,000 steps at a regular walking speed will walk about 2.=
15 miles, whilst a man of average height (5ft 9in) will walk about 2 =C2=BC=
 miles.
</p>



